{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/10351","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/10351/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/10351/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/10351/events","html_url":"https://github.com/curl/curl/issues/10351","id":1560553837,"node_id":"I_kwDOAAiu0c5dBClt","number":10351,"title":"Empty CURLOPT_CAINFO_BLOB causes error","user":{"login":"jay","id":965580,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk2NTU4MA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/965580?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay","html_url":"https://github.com/jay","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jay/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":184118197,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxODQxMTgxOTc=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/labels/regression","name":"regression","color":"33aa3f","default":false,"description":null},{"id":184118221,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxODQxMTgyMjE=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/labels/TLS","name":"TLS","color":"bfdadc","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":11,"created_at":"2023-01-27T23:18:34Z","updated_at":"2023-01-31T10:11:17Z","closed_at":"2023-01-31T10:11:17Z","author_association":"MEMBER","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### I did this\r\n\r\n@pgroke-dt [reported](https://curl.se/mail/lib-2023-01/0070.html) on the mailing list that, for curl 7.87.0 w/ OpenSSL backend, setting CURLOPT_CAINFO_BLOB to an empty string causes an error when peer verification is disabled.\r\n\r\nThe CA blob import function expects \"[one or more certificates](https://curl.se/libcurl/c/CURLOPT_CAINFO_BLOB.html)\" and returns an error if no certificate is read:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/curl/curl/blob/c12fb3ddaf48e709a7a4deaa55ec485e4df163ee/lib/vtls/openssl.c#L3077-L3078\r\n\r\nIn 7.86.0 ossl_connect_step1 calls load_cacert_from_memory directly and ignores the result if peer verification is disabled. Since then, certificate caching support was added in 3c16697e. Now in 7.87.0 ossl_connect_step1 calls Curl_ssl_setup_x509_store which calls load_cacert_from_memory, but does not ignore the result.\r\n\r\n### I expected the following\r\n\r\nMy first impression is this isn't a bug however AFAICT all other SSL backends that support CA blob either skip loading or ignore a bad load when peer verification is disabled.\r\n\r\n### curl/libcurl version\r\n\r\ncurl 7.87.1-DEV (i386-pc-win32) libcurl/7.87.1-DEV OpenSSL/1.1.1s nghttp2/1.50.0\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n/cc @gvollant @tlsa @icing ","closed_by":{"login":"bagder","id":177011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3NzAxMQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/177011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder","html_url":"https://github.com/bagder","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscri